ia dianjurkan oleh saudagar terhebat

00:33:50.720 --> 00:33:51.520
di bawah langit,

00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:53.310
taikun terbesar di ibu negara,

00:33:53.310 --> 00:33:54.270
Li Juta,

00:33:54.510 --> 00:33:56.400
Cikgu Li Wantang.

00:33:56.960 --> 00:33:58.220
Kebetulan begitu

00:33:58.510 --> 00:34:00.400
hari lahir Permaisuri Janda
semakin hampir,

00:34:00.400 --> 00:34:01.270
dan Maharaja muda

00:34:01.270 --> 00:34:02.960
ingin menggembirakan ibunya.

